# Stage: verify — run the deterministic checks

## Goal

Produce a machine-verifiable `verify-report.json` covering build / lint /
unit / integration / e2e / security checks. Every failed assertion MUST
have a runnable `repro` command. Verify is the G-v gate before review.

Verify is DETERMINISTIC: it MUST NOT use generative judgment. Every
finding either passes or fails based on a runnable command. If a check
can't be expressed as a command, it doesn't belong in verify (it
belongs in review).

